description:
Narrow footbridge forms a path, winding its way forward horizontally to the theatre stage, hidden deep in the cave. A viking maiden walks down the bridge, neither dressed nor naked. Just a glimpse of light scattered across the path — beads of moisture collect in the ropes of her fishing net gown, glistening in the low light of the cave as she moves forward. 

Soundscape created by PAN BONKA

{2020 — chapter 1 of 3}
